===Noun===
'''knot''' (plural: [[knots]])

#string, dough or similar long substance looped in on itself to produce a tied piece of material.
#string tied to a post or a similar item.
#(or hair etc) a clump.
#a maze-like pattern.
#a difficult situation. ''got into a knot''.
#a measurement of speed.

